dcterms:description: The United Nations food and agriculture trade dataset contains statistics on all food and agriculture products that are imported or exported annually by all countries worldwide. It represents a weighted, directed food and agriculture trading graph among 181 nations, spanning from 1986 to 2017, with around 500,000 edges. The edge weights indicate the total sum of normalized agriculture import or export values between two countries.
dcterms:title: UN Trade dataset
